        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Family Papers (.5 linear feet) series contains information about the different branches of the Ludwig family. The collection includes genealogies, histories, letters, and newspaper clippings about the Ludwig and Newman families. A particularly rich resource in this series is a notebook which outlines the history of the Ludwig family since the family first arrived in the United States. Each section of the notebook describes a branch of the Ludwig family, creating a detailed family history.</p>
