          <unittitle>Frederick E. Ludwig <unitdate type="inclusive" normal="1933/1985">1933-1985</unitdate>, <unitdate type="inclusive" normal="2001">2001</unitdate></unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Frederick E. Ludwig (2.0 linear feet) series is a rich source of information about the life and activities of Frederick E. Ludwig. It includes information on his activities as a bird bander, his life in the Navy, and his work as a physician. The Personal Papers sub-series includes his autobiography, as well as a manuscript entitled "Out of this World" which describes Frederick Ludwig's experiences in WWII. Papers included in the Professional Papers sub-series pertain to Ludwig's medical practice and his activities as a physician. These include a description of the burn treatment which he developed during WWII. The World War II sub-series consists of essays about his World War II experiences and scores of letters that he wrote to his wife.</p>
